snippet.textDisplay: While there is no disputing Rohail Hyatt's genius, I just don't get the hate for Strings that crops up in online comments and CS articles - IMHO, songs like "Sab Maya Hai" and "Naina Moray" are absolutely incredible musical gems.  This song....just wow! And although Sanwal's singing is beautiful and clear, the magic of Lala Sahib's inimitable voice is something else altogether. His 'ishq pawaiyan zanjeera' cuts right to my very soul.
